{"title":"英雄瞻仰英雄碑","authors":["顾工"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":9,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄瞻仰英雄碑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顾工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有三位英雄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都高挺前胸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在光辉的节日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在北京相逢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们有的捉过海盗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的培育出新的麦种，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的改进轧钢的机器，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们都获得伟大成功。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这三位英雄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步伐非常齐整，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来到英雄纪念碑前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞻仰浮雕上的斗争。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热浪在心中翻滚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热力在身上翻涌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那刻在碑上的火把呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更照亮他们的眼瞳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碑上的英雄一跃而下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把手中的火把相赠："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“儿女们，英雄们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝贺你们面迎万里东风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“接过这支火把吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去烧尽旧世界的灰尘；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接过这支火把吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去照亮全世界的星辰。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三位英雄朗朗大笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑声象凯旋的歌声："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“接过你们的火把出征，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们永远百战百胜！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这三位英雄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步伐非常齐整，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从英雄纪念碑前出发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走向更广阔的社会主义前程……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}